data.title: Bowling, Mah Jong, & More
data.text:
Bowling League Every Thursday

at 3:30 PM

at Millsboro Lanes

We have formed a league,

but can always add new bowlers!

Regardless of your bowling prowess,

come join us each Thursday.

The cost is only $9.00 per week to bowl.

All bowlers must be fully vaccinated.

If interested, please contact

Leslie Gladstone at

llgatty@gmail.com.

Mahjong Every Tuesday

at 1:00 PM

at Seaside

Current Seaside Members

are welcome to play

every Tuesday.

If you have a mahjong set,

please bring it.

One-time registration is required

(via email to Sara Rosen at

boysies.rosen@gmail.com).

International Student

Outreach Program

at Epworth United Methodist Church

Every Tuesday,

June 11 through September 3

5:00 PM- 7:00 PM

International Student

Outreach Program

Feeds hundreds of international students who work in our area

during the summer.

Epworth provides the meals and

Seaside provides the fruit and desserts.

We welcome you to stop in during the summer to participate in this wonderful opportunity to meet and talk to students from all over the world.

We are always in need of extra desserts.

The students particularly love fruit pies

and anything with chocolate.

Desserts can be dropped off

at Epworth

any time after 1:00 pm.

If you have any questions

about this program,

please contact Phyllis Bloom at prsbloom1228@gmail.com
